OL,3,CZoo launches dating profile to find
OL,4,Cmate for 'world's loneliest fish'
OL,6,FBristol Zoo Project has launched a
OL,7,Fdating profile for what they believe
OL,8,Fcould be the "world's loneliest fish".
OL,10,F"Konia" is named after a small group
OL,11,Fof critically endangered cichlid fish,
OL,12,Fthat come from Lake Barombi Mbo in
OL,13,Fwestern Cameroon.
OL,15,FZoo staff believe they may have the
OL,16,Fonly recorded Konia in accredited zoos
OL,17,Fworldwide. So they're appealing for
OL,18,Fsome "friends" to help their fish
OL,19,Fstart a family.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/3
