OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1784373494
OL,3,CZoo launches dating profile to find
OL,4,Cmate for 'world's loneliest fish'
OL,6,FThey wrote on Facebook: "If you know
OL,7,Fof a zoo, aquarium or specialist fish
OL,8,Fkeeper who may have Konia eisentrauti
OL,9,Fcichlids, please send them our way so
OL,10,Fwe can save this species!"
OL,12,FSo, what does Konia have to offer?
OL,13,FWell they're described as a five-year-
OL,14,Fold professional swimmer looking for a
OL,15,Fshort-term, open relationship.
OL,17,FThe profile says: "I love long swims
OL,18,F(I'm always on the move) playing hide
OL,19,Fand seek and chilling at home with my
OL,20,Fmany, many friends...
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/3
